These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Sport: snowboarding, golf, skiing, rugby
Birthday: october, november, may, july
1. Birthday:november is on the left of Birthday:october##1
2. Sport:snowboarding == Birthday:july##1
3. Birthday:may is on the right of Birthday:october##1
4. Sport:golf is on the left of Birthday:july##1
5. Sport:rugby is on the left of Birthday:october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | rugby | skiing | golf | snowboarding   |
| Birthday   | november  | october     | may   | july |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Flower: daisy, marigold, azalea, orchid
Cigar: alhambra, dannemann, tiparillo, old-henry
1. Flower:orchid == Cigar:dannemann##1
2. Flower:daisy is on the far right##1
3. Flower:marigold is on the right of Flower:orchid##1
4. Flower:orchid is on the right of Cigar:tiparillo##1
5. Cigar:dannemann is on the left of Cigar:alhambra##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | azalea | orchid | marigold | daisy    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo    | dannemann      | alhambra | old-henry |

